  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="KT347-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">poruḷ valikkum neñciṟkut talaimakaṉ collic celavaḻuṅkiyatu. </p>


        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">HE dispensing with going, speaking to [his] heart that
          strives after wealth. </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="KT347">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> malkucuṉai pularnta nalkūr curamutaṟ</l>
          <l> kumari vākaik kōluṭai naṟuvī</l>
          <l> maṭamāt tōkaik kuṭumiyiṟ ṟōṉṟuṅ</l>
          <l> kāṉa nīḷiṭait tāṉu nammō</l>
          <l> ṭoṉṟumaṇañ ceytaṉa ḷivaḷeṉiṉ</l>
          <l> ṉaṉṟē neñca nayantaniṉ ṟuṇivē.</l>


        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l rend="indent2">When [you] consider that she has made the one union</l>
          <l rend="indent">with us, also she herself , on the long forest way ,</l>
          <l rend="indent2">where the stalked fragrant blossom of the maiden Sirissa</l>
          <l rend="indent2">appears like the crest of a youthful big peacock,</l>
          <l rend="indent">in the poor desert, where plentiful mountain pools have dried up,</l>
          <l>– good [is], heart, your decision that you longed for .</l>

          <lg type="alternate" sameAs="5b" resp="#TVG">
            <l>If you considered that she would make the one union with us</l>

          </lg>
        </lg>

      </div>
    </body>
